\intbl \ql \b Background\b0 \line The Independent Institute of Education \'28Pty\'29 Ltd is registered with the Department of Higher Education and Training as a private higher education institution\'2C and is accredited to offer higher education programmes by the HEQC. It has applied for the accreditation of a Diploma in Business Accounting\'2C a HC in Public Management\'2C a Bachelor of Arts in Fashion Design\'2C  a Bachelor of Arts in Graphic Design\'2C  and a Bachelor of Arts in Interior Design\'2C among others. \cell \pard 

